 {row, column, row-reverse, column-reverse}
 row-reverse  (It reverses the direction in reverse direction) and column-reverse
# align-content -  is used to align the flex item vertically. It only has effect when flex items wrap onto multiple lines. {The values are stretch(default), center, flex-start, flex-end, space-between, space-evenly, space-around} 
